snippet.title: Asylum Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer of Asylum, the upcoming horror adventure from Senscape where players will be able to explore at leisure a vast and vivid asylum known as the Hanwell Mental Institute, while diving into a disturbing horror storyline unlike anything that has ever been experienced before in the adventure genre.
